				<AnimatedText 
					client:load
					text="Nerdy Stuff"
					type="split"
				/>
			</h1>
			<p class="text-center text-stone-600 dark:text-stone-300 mb-12 text-lg font-light">
				Welcome! This site was a passion project—I built it myself with modern web technologies to make sure all the details for our big day are easy for you to find.			</p>

